2:
Prevent me from dying now because I am loyal to you;
\q2 save me because I serve you and I trust in you, my God.
\q1

5:
Lord, you are good to us, and you forgive us;
\q1 you faithfully love very much all those who pray to you.
\q1

6:
Yahweh, listen to my prayer;
\q2 hear me when I cry out to you to help me.
\q1

14:
But God, proud men are trying to attack me;
\q2 a gang of cruel men are wanting to kill me;
\q2 they are men who do not have any respect for you.
\q1

15:
But Lord, you always act mercifully and kindly;
\q2 you do not become angry quickly;
\q2 you faithfully love us very much
\q2 and always do for us what you have promised to do.
\q1

17:
Yahweh, do something to show me that you are being good to me
\q2 so that those who hate me will see that you have encouraged me and helped me;
\q2 as a result, they will be ashamed.
